    <div><p>Goro Majima from the <em>Yakuza</em> / <em><a title="Series > Yakuza (Like a Dragon) [61 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/yakuza">Like a Dragon</a></em> series will appear as the final guest villain in the “<a title="Companies > SEGA [2,707 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> Villains Stage” downloadable content included with the Deluxe Edition of <em><a title="Games > SHINOBI: Art of Vengeance [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/shinobi-art-of-vengeance">SHINOBI: Art of Vengeance</a></em>, publisher SEGA and developer <a title="Companies > Lizardcube [44 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/lizardcube">Lizardcube</a> announced. <span id="more-1000539"></span></p><p>As previously announced <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/shinobi-art-of-vengeance-dlc-sega-villains-stage-adds-dr-eggman">Dr. Eggman from the <em>Sonic the Hedgehog</em> series</a> and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/shinobi-art-of-vengeance-dlc-sega-villains-stage-adds-death-adder">Death Adder from the <em>Golden Axe</em> series</a> will also appear.</p><p>The downloadable content is due out in early 2026.</p><p><em>SHINOBI: Art of Vengeance</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,630 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,115 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,447 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, Xbox Series, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,834 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,560 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2361770/SHINOBI_Art_of_Vengeance/" target="_blank">Steam</a>.</p></div>

        
    
